Reggae-blues singer, Harry Tare Okiri, popularly known as Mr. Harrysong is set to wed his fiancée, Alexer Peres Gopa on the 27th of March 2021 The singer made this announcement on Thursday, February 4 2021 in a post he shared on his Instagram handle. The wedding is scheduled to take place on the 27th of March 2021 in Warri, Delta state. He also uploaded his wedding invitation card that showed details of the event venue and colour of the day. Harrysong wrote: “ALL SHADES I got it perfect this time. March 27th at the KFT event center Warri delta state. Photo by @kolexor #tarex2021.”